    "long_instructions": "<br/>\r\n\r\n**Do This:** Read through the solution options in the table below. Choose one AI-powered solution you think your school's encrypted messaging app should use. Then, defend your choice using at least one potential benefit and one tradeoff from the chart.\r\n\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n  <thead>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <th><strong>AI-Powered Solution</strong></th>\r\n      <th><strong>Potential Benefits</strong></th>\r\n      <th><strong>Possible Tradeoffs / Risks</strong></th>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </thead>\r\n  <tbody>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td><strong>1. Use AI to flag harmful behavior using metadata</strong></td>\r\n      <td>\r\n        - Detects threats early<br>\r\n        - Helps schools prevent harm<br>\r\n        - Doesn’t require reading content <br><br>\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td>\r\n        - Could flag innocent conversations<br>\r\n        - May rely on biased patterns<br>\r\n        - Lacks full context\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td><strong>2. Let students opt-in or out of metadata scanning</strong></td>\r\n      <td>\r\n        - Respects user choice<br>\r\n        - Builds trust in the system\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td>\r\n        - Less effective for full protection<br>\r\n        - Could make policy confusing\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td><strong>3. Train AI on local (school-specific) examples</strong></td>\r\n      <td>\r\n        - More relevant results<br>\r\n        - May reduce false flags\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td>\r\n        - Could reinforce local bias<br>\r\n        - Still lacks full message content\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td><strong>4. Block metadata collection entirely</strong></td>\r\n      <td>\r\n        - Maximizes privacy<br>\r\n        - Reduces misuse risks\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td>\r\n        - Makes it harder to detect harmful patterns<br>\r\n        - Could limit school safety tools\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td><strong>5. Allow AI to flag, but always require human review</strong></td>\r\n      <td>\r\n        - Adds human judgment<br>\r\n        - Reduces false alarms\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td>\r\n        - Slows response time<br>\r\n        - Requires more staff time/training\r\n      </td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n\r\n<br/><br/>"
  },
